object: Area : Defines control areas and power exchanges between them
Circuit : Represents transmission circuit (replaced by TransmissionLine object
CSP : Models Concentrated Solar Power plants
Demand : Configures energy demand (linked with Demand Segments)
ExpansionAssociated : Adds related assets to expansion
Interconnection : Models inter-area or inter-systems connections
PaymentSchedule : Defines payment schedules in OPTGEN
RenewablePlant :Models renewable plants in SDDP, NCP, OPTGEN, and TSL.
RenewableStation :Groups renewable units in SDDP and NCP
ReserveGeneration:Models reserve generation in SDDP and NCP.
SeriesCapacitor: Models series capacitors in SDDP.
SupplyChainFixedConverter :Defines fixed commodities converter types in SDDP
SupplyChainFixedConverterCommodity :Defines fixed converter's commodity types in SDDP.
System :Defines system-wide settings in SDDP, NCP, and OPTGEN
TargetGeneration :Sets target generation in SDDP and NCP
ThermalGenerator :Models thermal generators in SDDP and NCP
ThermalPlant :Represents thermal plants in SDDP, NCP, and OPTGEN
TwoTerminalDCLink: Models 2-terminal DC links in SDDP(Replaced by ACInterconnection)
VSCConverter: Represents VSC converters in SDDP.
Study : Encapsulates full model setup in SDDP
